16 WHEREAS, Mr. Donley's spirit and love for music has inspired many members of the Holly
17 Springs and Hickory Flat communities to become better musicians and better people,
18 including Bryce Leatherwood, the 2022 winner of The Voice, who cited Mr. Donley as one
19 of his greatest inspirations; and
20 WHEREAS, beyond his love for music, Mr. Donley is remembered as an avid fisherman
21 who found enjoyment in sharing his hobby with others; and
22 WHEREAS, Mr. Donley will be forever remembered as a loving husband, father, and
23 beloved citizen of Cherokee County and it is abundantly fitting and proper that this
24 remarkable and distinguished Georgian be recognized appropriately by dedicating a road in
25 his memory.
26 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
27 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the portion of State Route 140 from Darnell Road to East
28 Cherokee Drive in Cherokee County is dedicated as the David Allen Donley Memorial
29 Parkway.
30 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
31 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the David Allen Donley Memorial
32 Parkway.
33 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
34 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
35 family of Mr. David Allen Donley and to the Department of Transportation.
